  , we adopt the row 0 containing zeros everywhere except the first position, such that

  
    
      
        f
        (
        x
        
          )
          
            0
          
        
        =
        1
        =
        
          ∑
          
            k
            =
            0
          
          
            ∞
          
        
        M
        [
        f
        
          ]
          
            0
            ,
            k
          
        
        
          x
          
            k
          
        
